Eugenie Bouchard survived a tough first set and then found another gear to beat Silvia Soler-Espinosa on Thursday.

The 20-year-old Canadian is fast emerging as one of the new stars of tennis and she didn't disappoint her fans - known as the Genie Army - eventually sealing a 7-5, 6-1 win.

